<p class="c3"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 624.00px; height: 624.00px;">
<img alt="artists impression of the restaurant car with fish menu" src="/assets/image2-4aa7e66357b9afd63bd84bbf43f549ad205f12b3a9a797ba39c3015117edae7c.png" width="624" height="624" />
</span><span class="c8 c27"><br><br></span><span class="c12">Exterior Design</span></p><p class="c20 c3"><span class="c17">The train boasts the distinctive double-decker design, known for its sleek profile and high-speed performance. Its exterior is wrapped in a vibrant livery that combines eye-catching stylish colours with subtle, elegant accents inspired by the LyM&aacute;&rsquo;s branding. This mix highlights both the train&#39;s high-speed capabilities and its focus on night travel.</span></p><p class="c20 c1"><span class="c17"></span></p><h3 class="c20 c22" id="h.r4drbj79uwct"><span class="c12">Interior Comfort and Amenities</span></h3><p class="c20 c3"><span class="c13">Seating and Sleeping Compartments:</span></p><ul class="c11 lst-kix_fn03p71rwisq-0 start"><li class="c9 c3 li-bullet-0"><span class="c13">The lower deck offers spacious seating arrangements, with options ranging from premium recliners to private cabins, blending efficiency with contemporary comfort. These areas feature adjustable lighting, power outlets, and privacy features, such as curtains and soundproofing.</span></li><li class="c9 c3 li-bullet-0"><span class="c13">The upper deck houses luxurious sleeping compartments, inspired by the Nightjet&#39;s deluxe offerings. Each compartment includes comfortable beds, high-quality linens, and en suite facilities, such as a private bathroom with a shower.</span></li></ul><p class="c20 c3"><span class="c13">Dining and Lounge Areas:</span></p><ul class="c11 lst-kix_x0hbo2gb1q3s-0 start"><li class="c9 c3 li-bullet-0"><span class="c13">A bistro-car on the lower deck serves a selection of gourmet meals, snacks, and beverages, catering to all tastes with a focus on local, sustainable ingredients.</span></li><li class="c3 c9 li-bullet-0"><span class="c13">The train includes a lounge area where passengers can enjoy a relaxed atmosphere, with large windows offering panoramic views of the passing scenery. This space draws inspiration from the Nightjet&rsquo;s focus on passenger experience, providing a social area for travellers to unwind.</span></li></ul><p class="c20 c3"><span class="c13">Sustainability and Technology:</span></p><ul class="c11 lst-kix_crynlzbmz2bq-0 start"><li class="c9 c3 li-bullet-0"><span class="c13">Emphasising sustainability, the train incorporates state-of-the-art green technologies, including energy-efficient propulsion and smart systems to minimise its environmental footprint.</span></li><li class="c9 c3 li-bullet-0"><span class="c13">Advanced onboard technology ensures a seamless travel experience, with free high-speed WiFi, an entertainment system accessible via personal devices, and real-time travel information.</span></li></ul>


