<h3 class="c20 c22" id="h.u464h3s40mnr"><span class="c12">Services</span></h3><ul class="c11 lst-kix_kbxz6m4xqq73-0 start"><li class="c9 c3 li-bullet-0"><span class="c17">Recognizing the importance of comfort on overnight journeys, the train offers amenities such as a welcome kit with sleep masks, earplugs, and eco-friendly toiletries.</span></li><li class="c9 c3 li-bullet-0"><span class="c17">Attentive, multilingual staff are available to assist passengers, ensuring a high level of service throughout the trip.</span></li><li class="c9 c3 li-bullet-0"><span class="c17">From 7 AM, a gourmet breakfast service is available, featuring a variety of options to cater to different dietary preferences, emphasising a fresh start to the day.</span></li></ul><p class="c20 c1"><span class="c5"></span></p><p class="c20 c3"><span class="c5">This train combines the best of high-speed rail and overnight travel, offering passengers a comfortable, efficient, and environmentally friendly way to traverse long distances. It represents a leap forward in train travel, marrying speed with luxury in a way that appeals to both business and leisure travellers and furthers Europe in meeting its climate goals, given the 20x less CO2 pollution created by night trains.</span></p><p class="c1 c20"><span class="c5"></span></p><p class="c20 c1"><span class="c5"></span></p><p class="c3"><span class="c8"><br> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="c10">LyM&aacute;<br></span><span class="c5">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Lyon - M&aacute;laga</span></p><p class="c3 c24"><span class="c5">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;22:00 - 08:00</span></p><p class="c3 c24"><span class="c5">&nbsp;27.12.2004 - 28.12.2024 </span></p><p class="c1 c24"><span class="c5"></span></p>

